-- U.S. Attorney Sues New York City Over Police Pension Calculation
-- B y   D o n   J e f f r e y
-- 2012-08-02T19:04:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-02/u-s-attorney-sues-new-york-city-over-police-pension-calculation.html
Manhattan U.S. Attorney Preet Bharara
said today his office sued the  New York  police department and
the city over the way they calculate pension benefits for police
officers who have served in the military since Sept. 11, 2001,
or will serve in the future.  To contact the reporter on this story:
